So you've chosen the §5§nWetware and Bioware Package§r for your newly purchased NAC™. A wise choice, as these are some of the most important circuits you will make. See the attached owner's manual for installation instructions.

§oGet it while you can! A two-for-one deal on circuit lines!§r

§n§lAccelerated Biological Coordinator Owner's Manual:§r

The NAC™ will track the most recent 100,000 circuits crafted, and can be calibrated to a specific circuit type by reaching a certain percentage of circuits of this type. At 60% (60,000) wetware circuits crafted, the NAC™ will become "fully calibrated" to wetware circuits, and the same applies to bioware circuits.

Depending on which calibration has been achieved, the Biological Coordinator will provide one of two bonuses:
- If calibrated to §nWetware§r, usage of Growth Catalyst Medium is reduced to zero
- If calibrated to §nBioware§r, usage of both Growth Catalyst Medium and Bio Catalyst Medium is reduced to zero
